item.title: DOFEN: Deep Oblivious Forest ENsemble
item.description: DOFEN: Deep Oblivious Forest Ensemble achieves state-of-the-art performance on tabular data by using a novel DNN architecture inspired by oblivious decision trees, surpassing other DNNs.
